description:
Authorities have identified 58-year-old Ryan Routh as the suspect in an assassination attempt on former President Donald Trump at his Florida Golf Course in West Palm Beach. KTLA's Carlos Saucedo details the latest in this developing investigation.

KTLA 5 News - Keeping Southern Californians informed since 1947.
